      "parameters": {
        "content": "## What to show in the recording\n\n- The OSuite credential uses `https://studio.osuite.ai` plus a workspace API key.\n- Review Planned Work creates a pre-execution action record.\n- The action does not proceed while approval is pending.\n- After approval, the business step runs and Record Final Outcome closes the evidence loop.\n- The OSuite replay URL proves what was requested, approved, executed, and recorded.",
